#: ../qml/About.qml:78
msgid "About Nix Manager:"
msgstr ""

#: ../qml/About.qml:86
msgid ""
"Nix Manager started as a Lomiri system settings plugin, but after UX "
"discussions it was decided to become a standalone app."
msgstr ""

#: ../qml/About.qml:95
msgid ""
"Nix Manager is a project that began in tandem with Crackle's adoption of "
"Nix. <br>I (ChromiumOS-Guy) developed the Python libraries Crackle uses to "
"interact with Nix, which is how this project started. <br>There’s a forum "
"post with more background: <br><a href=\"https://forums.ubports.com/"
"topic/11067/snap-pop-crackle-....and-nix-the-future-of-crackle/8?"
"_=1765038456437\">the forum post</a>"
msgstr ""

#: ../qml/About.qml:106
msgid ""
"This all culminated in this project, I hope you find it useful. \n"
"Nix Manager aims to make Nix more accessible, since using the terminal isn’t "
"always enjoyable on phone/tablet form factor."
msgstr ""

